OOC: its been a long time but ive decided to come back to the nbwrpg. Its 
like comin back home after a long vacation. Some of you may remember me some 
may not but im back and plan to have a little fun

    Destructor's circuits came online. He had been in sleep underneath the 
earth's crust for almost a year. His gears squeaked as they came into motion. 
His optical sensors came online. His hand sprung from the ground. He gripped 
hard and managed to pull himself out. His body was messed up pretty bad. He 
would need a new beast mode. He basically put himself into an automatic 
restart his body turned into a protoform type state. The black light emanated 
from him scanning for a body. It picked up a lion. He transformed into this 
new mode. Except for his Lion from had a  a black mane. He ran up the hill 
scanning for the nearest  predacon base. He sent out a distress signal with 
his location.

 Proto crawled out of his hole. His circuits had been frozen and he had been 
stuck in-between forms. (For all those unfamiliar with proto hes a rip off of 
that terminator 2 thing) He took the form of  a hawk and flew through the 
sky. (When proto is in an animal form which he needs to do every day at least 
twice to stay alive he has no more than the ability the animal gives him) His 
dark spark pulsated for destruction. He sent out a call for a predacon base 
to pick him up. (whoever wants a new recruit just be the first to answer.

  Galvatron awakened. Much to the dread of the planets. His silver dragon 
mode shined in the sunlight. It had been a long sleep but he was finally 
rejuvenated after his dreadful defeat by Optimus Prime. (in my last posts 
here me and another rpg'er had a nice battle between optimus prime and 
Galvatron which ended with both thier deaths) Even the his great spark could 
not keep him down. He would stay quiet for now. He would wait and watch the 
happenings of the planets before he reentered himself into it.


--part1_1a0.47d21e7.2a4fbc10_boundary
